@node wotznew "What's new in v1.40?!?!?!?!?"

The patching routines in v1.40 are now EVEN FASTER!!  and more intelligent!

You'll find that more programs are now rejected by the patcher routines, but
whatever is patched can now run up to 6 times faster than before!!!

Also, the command line handler is now fixed to remove "'s from the filename
so you can run NSA-Patch from a Dopus button.


None of the releases have made it to the aminet so far...  Either they've
all gone `missing' or Urban Muller is just ignoring them...  If this one
doesn't get put on there, then a lot of people will just lose out :(



@endnode
